Document: ArrayOccluder3D
Path: godot/classes/class_arrayoccluder3d.rst
Summary: Stores a 3D polygon shape for occlusion culling, similar to ArrayMesh but for occluders.

ArrayOccluder3D stores an arbitrary 3D polygon shape that can be used by the engine's occlusion culling system. This is analogous to ArrayMesh, but for occluders. See OccluderInstance3D's documentation for setup instructions.
