Summary: Properties for ArrayOccluder3D, including indices and vertices with their types and default values.

Property: indices (PackedInt32Array): Stores triangle indices for the occluder mesh. Default: PackedInt32Array()
Property: vertices (PackedVector3Array): Stores vertex positions for the occluder mesh. Default: PackedVector3Array()
